#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/camera/introduction.rst:5
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "简介"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/camera/introduction.rst:7
msgid ""
"A *Camera* is an object that provides a means of rendering images from "
"Blender. It defines which portion of a scene is visible in the rendered "
"image. By default a scene contains one camera. However, a scene can "
"contain more than one camera, but only one of them will be used at a "
"time. So you will only need to add a new camera if you are making cuts "
"between them. See :ref:`Animating Cameras <marker-bind-camera>`."
msgstr ""
"*摄像机* 物体，是Blender为渲染图像所提供的一种工具，用它来指定场景中哪个"
"部分是可见的而用以渲染，默认场景下包含一个摄像机。然而一个场景可以有多个"
"摄像机，但只有其中一个会被使用。如果你在减少场景对象时把他们删了的话，你"
"只需要再添加一个新的“摄像机”即可。请参阅 :ref:`动画相机<marker-bind-"
"camera>`."

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/camera/introduction.rst:16
msgid "Changing the Active Camera"
msgstr "改变活动摄像机"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/camera/introduction.rst:18
#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/camera/introduction.rst:51
msgid "Reference"
msgstr "参考"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/camera/introduction.rst
msgid "Mode:     Object Mode"
msgstr "模式： 物体模式"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/camera/introduction.rst
msgid "Hotkey:   :kbd:`Ctrl-Numpad0`"
msgstr "快捷键:   :kbd:`Ctrl-Numpad0`"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/camera/introduction.rst:26
msgid "Active camera (left one)."
msgstr "活动摄像机（左一）"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/camera/introduction.rst:29
msgid ""
"The *active* camera is the camera that is currently being used for "
"rendering and camera view :kbd:`Numpad0`."
msgstr "这个活动的摄像机目前用于渲染和相机视图 :kbd:`Numpad0`。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/camera/introduction.rst:32
msgid ""
"Select the camera you would like to make active and press :kbd:`Ctrl-"
"Numpad0` (by doing so, you also switch the view to camera view). In "
"order to render, each scene **must** have an active camera."
msgstr ""
"选择您想将其作为新的活动摄像机的摄像机，并按 :kbd:`Ctrl-Numpad0` （这样,"
"您也可以将视图切换到摄像机视图）。每个场景 **必须** 有一个活动摄像机用以"
"渲染。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/camera/introduction.rst:36
msgid ""
"The active camera can also be set in the *Scene* tab of the *Properties "
"Editor*."
msgstr "活动摄像机也可以通过 *属性编辑器* 中的 *场景* 选项卡设置。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/camera/introduction.rst:38
msgid ""
"The camera with the solid triangle on top is the active camera. Limit "
"and mist indicators of cameras are drawn darker if the camera is not the "
"active camera for the current scene."
msgstr ""
"活动摄像机上方的三角形是实心的，当前场景中受限制或者不是活动摄像机的摄像"
"机对象上方的三角形则是线框表示。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/camera/introduction.rst:43
msgid ""
"The active camera, as well as the layers, can be specific to a given "
"view, or global (locked) to the whole scene. See :doc:`Local Camera </"
"editors/3dview/properties/panels>`."
msgstr ""
"通过活动摄像机及图层可以是指定的视图，也可以是全局（锁定）到整个场景。请"
"参阅 :doc:`Local Camera </editors/3dview/properties/panels>`."

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/camera/introduction.rst:49
msgid "Render Border"
msgstr "渲染区域"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/camera/introduction.rst
msgid "Mode:     All modes"
msgstr "模式：所有模式"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/camera/introduction.rst
msgid "Menu:     :menuselection:`View --> Render Border`"
msgstr "菜单:      :menuselection:`视图 --> 渲染区域`"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/camera/introduction.rst
msgid "Hotkey:   :kbd:`Ctrl-B`"
msgstr "快捷键:   :kbd:`Ctrl-B`"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/camera/introduction.rst:61
msgid "Render Border toggle."
msgstr "图示选项进行切换。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/camera/introduction.rst:64
msgid ""
"While in camera view, you can define a subregion to render by drawing "
"out a rectangle within the camera's frame. Your renders will now be "
"limited to the part of scene visible within the render border. This can "
"be very useful for reducing render times for quick previews on an area "
"of interest."
msgstr ""
"在摄像机视图中，您可以通过在摄像机的框架内绘制一个矩形来定义要渲染的范"
"围。然后渲染将被限制在边界范围内的可见部分。这对缩短预览在感兴趣的区域的"
"渲染时间非常有帮助。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/camera/introduction.rst:68
msgid ""
"The border can be disabled by disabling the *Border* option in the "
"*Dimensions* panel in the *Render* tab or by activating the option again."
msgstr ""
"通过在 *渲染* 选项卡的 *规格尺寸* 面板中禁用 *边界范围* 选项或再次激活选"
"项，可以禁用范围。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/camera/introduction.rst:77
msgid ""
"When Render Border is activated, :doc:`Sampled Motion Blur </render/"
"blender_render/settings/motion_blur>` will become available to view in "
"the 3D View."
msgstr ""
"边界范围被激活时, :doc:`采样运动模糊 </render/blender_render/settings/"
"motion_blur>` 将可在3D视图中查看。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/camera/introduction.rst:80
msgid "Render border and associated render."
msgstr "边界范围和相关渲染。"
